text: "King George Street" is a 1986 song by British band Squeeze. It is the fourth and final single from their sixth studio album Cosi Fan Tutti Frutti and did not chart worldwide. ==Track listing== ;7" # "King George Street" (3:48) # "Love's Crashing Waves (live)" (4:17) ;12" # "King George Street" (3:48) # "Love's Crashing Waves (live)" (4:17) # "Up the Junction (live)" (3:20) == References == Category:1986 songs Category:Pop rock songs Category:Squeeze (band) songs
